Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.47,注释,,0,0,0,,翻译  1440kHz
Dialogue: 1,0:00:12.55,0:00:14.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,﻿派  在烤架上烤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.55,0:00:14.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pie, fried on the grill
Dialogue: 1,0:00:14.38,0:00:15.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就是天意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.38,0:00:15.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just as nature intended
Dialogue: 1,0:00:28.75,0:00:30.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  有没有看到我们的派
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.75,0:00:30.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, have you seen our pie?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:30.81,0:00:32.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们一整个早上都在烤这个派
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.81,0:00:32.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The one we spent all morning cooking
Dialogue: 1,0:00:32.99,0:00:33.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打算要送你的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.99,0:00:33.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just for you?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:33.81,0:00:35.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它一定会自己冒出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.81,0:00:35.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it'll turn up
Dialogue: 1,0:00:36.67,0:00:37.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.67,0:00:37.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:00:37.82,0:00:39.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到你的短裤了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.82,0:00:39.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We found your shorts
Dialogue: 1,0:00:39.15,0:00:40.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.15,0:00:40.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
